_:N69cae00db59543ea9c64cf20b9cc9264 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Lucy Powell was previously Lord President of the Council and Leader of the House of Commons from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Manchester Central in July 2024.</p>\n" .
